(58, 'woo-activation-survey-blockers-22AUG23', 'info', 'en_US', 'How can we help you get that first sale?', 'Your feedback is vital. Please take a minute to share your experience of setting up your new store and whether anything is preventing you from making those first few sales. Together, we can make Woo even better!', '{}', 'pending', 'woocommerce.com', '2023-10-25 08:06:39', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 0, 'info'),
